===Etymology===
From {{der|en|la|abstēmius||abstaining from wine}}; from {{m|la|ab}}, {{m|la|abs||from}} + {{m|la|tēmus}}, a root of {{m|la|tēmētum||[[intoxicating]] drink, especially strong mead or wine}} (possibly from {{der|en|ine-pro|*temH-||dark (referring to the colour of wine)}}) {{suffix|en||ous}}.<ref>Compare {{R:Oxford Dictionaries Online}}</ref>

